    <!-- author:   will@1dao2.com
         date:     2017/11/09
	 modified: 2017/11/16

         course table canvas:
         1920 x 1080

         sidebar      table         sidebar
         + ~~~ + ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ + ~~~ +
    week |100dp|      1400dp        |420dp|
         + ~~~ + ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ +     +
         |     |                    |     |
         |Time |    Course Table    |EMPTY|
         |     |                    |     |
           ... |       ...            ...
              2dp: divider line

         Table: 7 x 8 => 1400dp * 640dp

         Course Item: 200dp * 80dp
         200dp = 198dp + 2dp
         80dp  = 78dp  + 2dp

         Total canvas:
         (258dp + 2dp + 1400dp) * week-height * (2dp + 640dp)
     -->

